    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing around 50 species of trees and shrubs native to tropical America, yielding fragrant wood and valued as ornamentals, due to showy flowers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
